data.description: Lovely 4 bedroom, 2.5 baths in a quiet, serene setting of Ellenwood. Home includes a 2-car garage, separate living room (currently used as an office), separate dining room, kitchen, eat-in kitchen area, and large family room. All 4 bedrooms are upstairs including the largest primary bedroom to be found anywhere with a large en suite and walk-in closet. Large fenced-in backyard with new shed that can become a great workshop, storage shed or "she shed". Convenient to shopping and the interstate.
